history.content:
<md>Hey all, Web Design DeCal enrollment applications are open!

You know you're going to spend the Spring semester surfing the internet, especially when it's remote — why not spend some of this time learning how to make beautifully designed websites too? Come take the Web Design DeCal and learn to design and code a website from scratch!

Learn more at [wdd.io](wdd.io) and check out some awesome projects from past students at [webdesigndecal.github.io/showcase](webdesigndecal.github.io/showcase).

This 2-unit course will be held on Tuesdays 7:00 – 8:30 PM and Thursdays 7:00 – 8:00 PM PDT online (Zoom).

**Apply at [tinyurl.com/wdd-sp21](tinyurl.com/wdd-sp21) by Saturday, January 23rd, 2021 11:59 PM (PST).** This class is designed for beginners and all majors, no prior coding experience necessary. Hope to see you in class!

If you'd like to audit, there is no need to apply. We'll post recorded lectures on [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/user/wddlive) and you'll have access to course materials.</md>
history.subject: Web Design DeCal Sp21 Enrollment Applications Released!
